## IF ONLY ONE CHARACTER THEN JUST SET CHARACTER1. REST CAN BE NULL
## EVERY CHARACTER THAT USES THIS SCRIPT MUST BE SETUP IN HERE!!
## CASE SENSITIVE! CAPITAL FIRST LETTER - LOWER CASE REST
